name: Diamond
description: Diamonds are a form of carbon, made up of nearly 100% carbon atoms. The arrangement of the carbon atoms in a diamond's lattice gives it its unique properties.

name: Gold
description: Gold is a soft, dense, yellow metal that is malleable and ductile. It is also a good conductor of heat and electricity, and resists corrosion and tarnishing.

name: Platinum
description: Platinum is a chemical element with the symbol Pt and atomic number 78. It is a dense, malleable, ductile, highly unreactive, precious, silverish-white transition metal.

name: Gemstone
description: A gemstone is a material that can be cut and polished for use in jewelry or other ornamental applications. They are also known as fine gems, jewels, precious stones, or semiprecious stones.
